00:51:33,694 --> 00:51:36,959
I plan to unveil the electricity
at the coming nativity service.

791
00:51:36,960 --> 00:51:38,449
Herbert, your heart.

792
00:51:39,193 --> 00:51:40,393
Sit down, love.

793
00:51:40,394 --> 00:51:41,726
Aye.

794
00:51:41,726 --> 00:51:44,259
[DAVID] Please, think of
this with an open mind.

795
00:51:44,260 --> 00:51:48,859
Think of Herbert. No cumbersome
candles or lanterns to change.

796
00:51:48,860 --> 00:51:50,559
You of all people should
see the value in that.

797
00:51:50,559 --> 00:51:52,458
[ELEANOR]
You could use a lighter load.

798
00:51:52,459 --> 00:51:57,059
L...What'll I do with all
the Haddington candles?

799
00:51:57,060 --> 00:52:00,459
Well, <i>I...</i> I imagine that
we can return them.

800
00:52:00,459 --> 00:52:03,516
In fact, that's the
task that I'll gladly take on.

801
00:52:04,192 --> 00:52:06,750
[BEA] Oh, it's got to
be here somewhere.

802
00:52:08,793 --> 00:52:10,224
Edward!

803
00:52:12,359 --> 00:52:14,188
I have a feeling Edward.

804
00:52:15,459 --> 00:52:17,890
I have a feeling
this is the one.

