814
00:52:37,458 --> 00:52:39,224
But that's a standing order.

815
00:52:39,225 --> 00:52:41,282
It has been for
two hundred years.

816
00:52:41,792 --> 00:52:43,291
It's standing no more,
I'm afraid.

817
00:52:43,291 --> 00:52:45,457
But I just delivered
three crates.

