00:52:45,458 --> 00:52:48,257
Yes,thank you,
but we only need one.

819
00:52:48,258 --> 00:52:50,621
<i>But... but--</i>

820
00:52:50,758 --> 00:52:53,849
[DAVID] Trust me when I say,
