00:54:45,621 --> 00:54:53,611
♪ Jesus, Lord at thy birth. ♪

844
00:54:54,787 --> 00:55:04,778
♪ Jesus, Lord at thy birth. ♪

845
00:55:08,920 --> 00:55:13,409
In my short time in Gladbury,
I have seen many miracles.

846
00:55:13,887 --> 00:55:16,053
I have seen angels at work.

847
00:55:16,054 --> 00:55:20,520
I have seen them on the
rooftops, at kitchen tables,

848
00:55:20,520 --> 00:55:23,213
and in this very sanctuary.

849
00:55:23,520 --> 00:55:26,952
In fact, I see these angels now.

850
00:55:27,520 --> 00:55:29,418
Mr. Hardy Collins.

851
00:55:30,886 --> 00:55:32,579
Dear Ms. Leonard.

852
00:55:34,519 --> 00:55:38,186
Herbert Hopewell. And every
single one of you who has

