00:56:46,951 --> 00:56:48,746
[CHILD]
Mummy! Daddy!

866
00:56:54,018 --> 00:56:55,183
Get the children!

867
00:56:55,183 --> 00:56:56,774
[DAVID]
Everyone, please!

868
00:56:58,350 --> 00:56:59,850
Remain calm!

