965
01:06:06,400 --> 01:06:09,888
I'm finally making a name
for myself, for the family.

966
01:06:10,200 --> 01:06:11,999
Business is expanding,

967
01:06:12,000 --> 01:06:15,057
and one day I'll
introduce you to Priscilla.

968
01:06:19,333 --> 01:06:21,196
Why did you come?

969
01:06:31,399 --> 01:06:35,699
I know how much this candle
means to you, to Gladbury,

