01:06:43,832 --> 01:06:45,098
See what, Mother?

973
01:06:45,099 --> 01:06:46,599
A miracle?

974
01:06:46,599 --> 01:06:48,432
Gladbury needs you, son.

975
01:06:48,432 --> 01:06:50,198
The world needs me.

976
01:06:50,199 --> 01:06:54,188
I'm lighting up entire cities.

977
01:07:00,999 --> 01:07:03,032
It was good to see you.

978
01:07:03,032 --> 01:07:04,691
Both of you.

979
01:07:06,198 --> 01:07:08,255
